Thanks for using Calm! This update contains multiple bug fixes and performance improvements.

Be sure to listen to our newest Sleep Stories including “The Ocean Moon,” narrated by celebrated actress Laura Dern, where you’ll journey from the country to the coast alongside rolling trains and cresting waves. Or drift away to a selection of Calm Classics with one of our beloved narrators in the “Best of Alan Sklar - Anthology.” And don’t forget to listen to world-renowned actor Matthew McConaughey's dreamy story about the mysteries of the universe in “Wonder.”

Relax deeply and fall asleep peacefully with six tranquil music tracks from Liquid Mind by composer Chuck Wild.

Check out our popular meditation program by Jeff Warren, known for his dynamic and accessible style of teaching, titled “How to Meditate.” It's a simple 30-day program for everyone.

As always, you can expect an original Daily Calm every day, new Sleep Stories every week, and new meditation programs.

While you're waiting for the update to install, try this simple exercise: taking a deep breath in, say in your mind "breathing in, I am calm". Then breathing out, slowly, silently say "breathing out, I am peaceful". Continue this cycle for a few minutes, breathing in, I am calm... breathing out, I am peaceful. You can use this technique anytime you need a calming break in your day. Enjoy!
